text: Guillermo Pfaab (born 11 October 1968) is an Argentine rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Argentina Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Pan American Games medalists in rowing Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Argentina Category:Rowers at the 1995 Pan American Games Category:Rowers at the 1999 Pan American Games
